Package: liblingmoshellsurfaces1
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends:
 ${shlibs:Depends},
 ${misc:Depends},
Description: Lingmo Desktop shell surfaces library (runtime)
 LingmoShellSurfaces provides the visual shell layer for Lingmo Desktop,
 including Panel (top/bottom taskbar), Desktop (wallpaper/background), and
 Overview (window switcher/task view) surfaces built on wlr-layer-shell
 (Wayland) and EWMH (X11).
 .
 This package contains the shared library.

Package: liblingmoshellsurfaces-dev
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Section: libdevel
Depends:
 liblingmoshellsurfaces1 (= ${binary:Version}),
 qt6-base-dev,
 ${misc:Depends},
Description: Lingmo Desktop shell surfaces library (development)
 LingmoShellSurfaces provides the visual shell layer for Lingmo Desktop,
 including Panel (top/bottom taskbar), Desktop (wallpaper/background), and
 Overview (window switcher/task view) surfaces.
 .
 This package contains development headers and CMake modules.

Package: qml-module-lingmo-shell
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Section: libs
Depends:
 liblingmoshellsurfaces1 (= ${binary:Version}),
 qml6-module-qtquick,
 ${shlibs:Depends},
 ${misc:Depends},
Description: Lingmo Desktop shell surfaces QML plugin
 QML bindings for LingmoShellSurfaces, providing PanelSurfaceItem,
 DesktopSurfaceItem, and OverviewSurfaceItem types under Lingmo.Shell 1.0.
